# Dockhand Environment Variables
# This file serves as a template. Copy it to .env and fill in the actual values.

# Inherited from root .env (do not set here):
# - TZ: Timezone (inherited from root .env)
# - DOMAIN: Base domain name (inherited from root .env)

# Note: Dockhand uses SQLite by default with no additional configuration needed.
# The app store credentials and user data in /app/data volume.
